# @VERSION spec:gdla v:0.1.0 generated:2026-03-10 source:api-agent
# Project Atlas — legacy internal finance API surface (as-is)

@D legacy-finance-api|Acme legacy internal finance API|1.4.7|https://api.acme.internal/finance/v1

@AUTH internal_jwt|Internal JWT issued by Acme SSO|Authorization

@S JournalEntry|Legacy journal entry payload
 jeId|integer|required|int64|Primary key
 jeDate|string|required|date|Posting date
 accountRef|integer|required|int64|GeneralLedger account ID
 amount|number|required||Posted amount
 source|string|required||MANUAL|AUTO|REVERSAL|IMPORT|FX_REVAL
 createdBy|string|required||System or user that posted
 batchId|string|||Batch identifier when applicable

@S GeneralLedger|Legacy account payload
 accountId|integer|required|int64|Primary key
 code|string|required||Chart of accounts code
 name|string|||Display name
 status|string|required||ACTIVE|INACTIVE|SUSPENDED|ARCHIVED
 currency|string|required||ISO currency

@S ReconciliationRun|Reconciliation summary
 runId|integer|required|int64|Primary key
 period|string|required||YYYY-MM
 variance|number|||Total unreconciled variance
 status|string|required||SUCCESS|VARIANCE|FAILED|IN_PROGRESS

@EP GET /accounts|Lists active GeneralLedger accounts|listAccounts
@EP GET /accounts/{id}|Returns a single account by ID|getAccount
@EP GET /journal|Lists journal entries with filters|listJournalEntries
@EP POST /journal|Posts a new manual journal entry|createJournalEntry
@EP POST /journal/{id}/reverse|Reverses an existing entry|reverseJournalEntry
@EP GET /reconciliation/{period}|Returns reconciliation status for a period|getReconciliation
@EP POST /close/{period}|Triggers month-end close (long-running)|runMonthEndClose

@R JournalEntry -> GeneralLedger|references|JournalEntry posts against a GeneralLedger account
@R ReconciliationRun -> JournalEntry|aggregates|Reconciliation summarises a window of journal entries
